---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern-Style Beef Bowls with Creamy Hummus Dressing
description: Skip the pita and instead layer this wonderous bowl with all your favourite shawarma toppings: roasted carrots, sweet tomatoes, pickles, olives and a creamy hummus dressing!

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
